   Oak Ridge Reservation

   Oak Ridge facilities include manufacturing expertise, environmental
   restoration, cleanup technology development, waste management
   technology, project management, and education. Major sites at Oak Ridge
   include the Y-12 National Security Complex and the Oak Ridge National
   Laboratory. ORR is located in Roane County, Tennessee, about 7 miles
   from the center of the city of Oak Ridge and about 25 miles northwest
   of Knoxville.   Oak Ridge Reservation (Oak Ridge, TN)
